{"tid":550033,"cid":20,"subCid":0,"title":"係加拿大學緊做汽車 鍍膜,你問我答。","createTime":"2018-02-04T10:14:20.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-14T04:20:56.000Z","uid":63075,"like":21,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":40,"replies":[{"pid":"1fad757c0c6b5a7bb854dc394acbab7b7608ea00","tid":550033,"uid":63075,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-04T10:14:20.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.lifestyle.appledaily.com/lifestyle/car/daily/article/20160819/19742335\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.lifestyle.appledaily.com%2Flifestyle%2Fcar%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20160819%2F19742335&d=alaECXlSwFpfQY0npZXDsgdLCpCjoNGxXEizPMjNmRM%3D&h=80f5384a\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.lifestyle.appledaily.com%2Flifestyle%2Fcar%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20160819%2F19742335&h=a0acb08c\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.lifestyle.appledaily.com/lifestyle/car/daily/article/20160819/19742335</a><br />\n首先建議你地睇下哩段片<br />\n<br />\n利申  學左大半年   都係華人公司黎 (來自台灣 )<br />\n<br />\n我留意到香港哩幾年開左好撚多做鍍膜既公司<br />\n<br />\n有好多魚目混珠,呃飯食。如果你地對鍍膜有疑問<br />\n<br />\n可以係度問    我會同你分析 <br />\n<br />\n我亦都會話返比你地知   做鍍膜有咩要注意番既地方。<br />\n<br />\n同點先會唔比人呃, 點先算  貨真價實<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n唔會介紹你地去邊度做鍍膜   我淨係會話比你知邊間係呃錢/可疑"},{"pid":"b2f96eed08838977c29a3d600e41b24bef5c45aa","tid":550033,"uid":63075,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-04T10:18:09.000Z","msg":"如果你仲未知咩係鍍膜<br />\n<br />\n首先了解下<br />\n<a href=\"http://jerry8667.pixnet.net/blog/post/390715835-%E4%B8%83%E5%80%8B%E4%BD%A0%E5%BF%85%E9%A0%88%E8%A6%81%E7%9F%A5%E9%81%93%E9%8D%8D%E8%86%9C%E7%9F%A5%E8%AD%98\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fjerry8667.pixnet.net%2Fblog%2Fpost%2F390715835-%25E4%25B8%2583%25E5%2580%258B%25E4%25BD%25A0%25E5%25BF%2585%25E9%25A0%2588%25E8%25A6%2581%25E7%259F%25A5%25E9%2581%2593%25E9%258D%258D%25E8%2586%259C%25E7%259F%25A5%25E8%25AD%2598&d=alaECXlSwFpfQY0npZXDsgdLCpCjoNGxXEizPMjNmRM%3D&h=b7e672c8\" target=\"_blank\">http://jerry8667.pixnet.net/blog/post/390715835-%E4%B8%83%E5%80%8B%E4%BD%A0%E5%BF%85%E9%A0%88%E8%A6%81%E7%9F%A5%E9%81%93%E9%8D%8D%E8%86%9C%E7%9F%A5%E8%AD%98</a>"},{"pid":"ac5b26f0e22fdcc7f26bbccd27931fa3bfd46822","tid":550033,"uid":8100,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-04T10:20:02.000Z","msg":"用緊邊隻brand"},{"pid":"71d7e1297690bdfee7cad3203742648cd11f1992","tid":550033,"uid":63075,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ac5b26f0e22fdcc7f26bbccd27931fa3bfd46822","tid":550033,"uid":8100,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-04T10:20:02.000Z","msg":"用緊邊隻brand"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-04T10:33:25.000Z","msg":"公司仔黎  有分不同價錢  有做carpro ,gtechniq ,同台灣自家品牌"},{"pid":"74df917286f567c4d711bff9eb55ecd20ba359f0","tid":550033,"uid":10044,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-04T10:34:06.000Z","msg":"點先唔俾人呃<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a95bce6fbd362c53488b4af462a4473d27b4ba59","tid":550033,"uid":33004,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-04T10:38:54.000Z","msg":"好想去學wrap車<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n勁好呃<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"158e5840ed1a66b63a8bd27d5755aeafdd168ebf","tid":550033,"uid":13416,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-04T10:40:10.000Z","msg":"台灣係Kube bond?"},{"pid":"b7e9147fee49d6d3f4eb51716cbfa0295b9aa1d3","tid":550033,"uid":63075,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"74df917286f567c4d711bff9eb55ecd20ba359f0","tid":550033,"uid":10044,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-04T10:34:06.000Z","msg":"點先唔俾人呃<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-04T10:54:29.000Z","msg":"第一，梗係信譽啦　　　睇下佢間野成立左幾耐　口卑如何<br />\n<br />\n第二，要問清楚佢地邊隻鍍膜<br />\n<br />\n第三，自備捕紋燈／黃光電筒去驗收<br />\n<br />\n第四，用成本論，時間　去推斷佢係真定呃錢　　<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n幫一架非全新車做鍍膜　事前功夫，研磨　　細車都６個鐘起　　大車８個鐘起（講緊１至２個師傅）<br />\n一日可能只係做到１架／２架車<br />\n<br />\n你買既係佢事前功夫，研磨手勢　而唔係單單同你上鍍膜咁簡單<br />\n<br />\n而且每一層鍍膜　唔照燈　需要１至２日時間去乾先可以上第二層<br />\n<br />\n你覺得２千蚊都唔洗　會交到Ｄ咩貨比你？"},{"pid":"31390c1296358e08d4a5f294ab93b211a4ee925a","tid":550033,"uid":63075,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-04T11:04:08.000Z","msg":"其實你地比一萬/幾千人地去幫你做鍍膜<br />\n<br />\n鍍膜施工成本  可能只係佔哩筆錢既5分1 ,甚至更少<br />\n<br />\n全車上鍍膜  快則1個鐘多D,慢既  2個鐘多D  實做完  <br />\n<br />\n而支鍍膜 值得幾多錢? 當然平可以平到幾百蚊都有支   貴 幾千蚊都有(自己上淘寶搵下就知)<br />\n<br />\n就依家香港流行緊用gtechniq <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://sep.yimg.com/ay/autogeek/gtechniq-exo-and-csl-kit-33.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fsep.yimg.com%2Fay%2Fautogeek%2Fgtechniq-exo-and-csl-kit-33.gif&h=5a9547c8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n哩隻都加埋疏水層   姐係所謂既複合鍛膜   成本大約1千多D<br />\n<br />\n但就收你5千幾6千   <br />\n<br />\n你地大部分既錢  係用黎支付師傅幫你執返好架車既人工錢<br />\n<br />\n因為做鍍膜最重要就係事前功夫<br />\n<br />\n若果做得唔好   咁果D花痕,污穢,氧化物  就會藏左係鍛膜下面   你點省點洗都無用<br />\n<br />\n事後要搵人執番   又要幾千 。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n你比幾千蚊人，主要係買 <span style=\"color: red;\">人地幫你執返靚架車,打好個底</span>　再上鍍膜。<br />\n<br />\n所以一定要注意佢地事前功夫包含左咩　　<br />\n<br />\n最值錢一定係哩D功夫 : <strong><span style=\"color: red;\">除太陽紋,淡化花痕,去水積,去氧化層 還原基本色<br />\n</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n如果只係話 咩包  全車去漬<br />\n<br />\n而<span style=\"color: red;\">無清楚列明 包去除太陽紋,淡化花痕</span><br />\n<br />\n避重就輕     咁你可以慳返D錢都得   自己去比1千蚊人地打下蠟好撚過"},{"pid":"cdc6fcd56eea569d6e60cd6bc93bb959835bef12","tid":550033,"uid":16058,"like":0,"dislike":4,"score":-4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-04T11:04:11.000Z","msg":"不如巴打你直接D講下邊D係混水摸魚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"60683f12f59eeeb2cad87d6a13a292153ebeb84e","tid":550033,"uid":63075,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-04T11:04:59.000Z","msg":"至於  何為太陽紋<br />\n<br />\n可以睇下哩度<a href=\"http://kdetailing.pixnet.net/blog/post/27260958-%E6%B1%BD%E8%BB%8A%E7%BE%8E%E5%AE%B9diy.%E5%A4%AA%E9%99%BD%E7%B4%8B%E5%BD%A2%E6%88%90%E7%9A%84%E5%8E%9F%E5%9B%A0.k-detailing\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fkdetailing.pixnet.net%2Fblog%2Fpost%2F27260958-%25E6%25B1%25BD%25E8%25BB%258A%25E7%25BE%258E%25E5%25AE%25B9diy.%25E5%25A4%25AA%25E9%2599%25BD%25E7%25B4%258B%25E5%25BD%25A2%25E6%2588%2590%25E7%259A%2584%25E5%258E%259F%25E5%259B%25A0.k-detailing&d=alaECXlSwFpfQY0npZXDsgdLCpCjoNGxXEizPMjNmRM%3D&h=167174e3\" target=\"_blank\">http://kdetailing.pixnet.net/blog/post/27260958-%E6%B1%BD%E8%BB%8A%E7%BE%8E%E5%AE%B9diy.%E5%A4%AA%E9%99%BD%E7%B4%8B%E5%BD%A2%E6%88%90%E7%9A%84%E5%8E%9F%E5%9B%A0.k-detailing</a>"},{"pid":"edf7f19492079e8c0bf5833d5e49835c5fcbe356","tid":550033,"uid":63075,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"quote":{"pid":"cdc6fcd56eea569d6e60cd6bc93bb959835bef12","tid":550033,"uid":16058,"like":0,"dislike":4,"score":-4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-04T11:04:11.000Z","msg":"不如巴打你直接D講下邊D係混水摸魚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-04T11:11:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/02/04/190904_f753c3a75140ef4445b7e6826161c842.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F02%2F04%2F190904_f753c3a75140ef4445b7e6826161c842.png&h=b0592eac&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">屌你老母 12H?<br />\n屌你老母  5層?<br />\n又淨係話去漬</span>"},{"pid":"78482907efdfbd7bc8a8c9e1885b4a560b10d39d","tid":550033,"uid":132038,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-04T11:13:25.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"a84c624c9e93a5e358b8626764e64d701cd5e442","tid":550033,"uid":63075,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-04T11:14:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/02/04/191222_f753c3a75140ef4445b7e6826161c842.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F02%2F04%2F191222_f753c3a75140ef4445b7e6826161c842.png&h=82a9d640&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n又係淨係話去漬<br />\n<br />\n4層蠟打底?嘩....大佬你要脫脂架   你要去撚左D蠟先上鍍膜架"},{"pid":"804085c32b5b05d6b9f83e83c24a3bf7ae6af20d","tid":550033,"uid":16058,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"quote":{"pid":"edf7f19492079e8c0bf5833d5e49835c5fcbe356","tid":550033,"uid":63075,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"quote":{"pid":"cdc6fcd56eea569d6e60cd6bc93bb959835bef12","tid":550033,"uid":16058,"like":0,"dislike":4,"score":-4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-04T11:04:11.000Z","msg":"不如巴打你直接D講下邊D係混水摸魚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-04T11:11:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/02/04/190904_f753c3a75140ef4445b7e6826161c842.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F02%2F04%2F190904_f753c3a75140ef4445b7e6826161c842.png&h=b0592eac&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">屌你老母 12H?<br />\n屌你老母  5層?<br />\n又淨係話去漬</span>"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-04T11:15:14.000Z","msg":"咁咪幾好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n歡迎巴打爆多D 咪比D奸商賺到笑"},{"pid":"b87c1a62ae0ec6edb7d036d816c7fff31cb28120","tid":550033,"uid":16058,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-04T11:17:12.000Z","msg":"巴打點睇鍍晶XX<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ?搵火堅唔堅其實 好驚只係GIMMIK野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0e0ea82c71d860f5584aed3ff11d44a17ff80a7d","tid":550033,"uid":63075,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"78482907efdfbd7bc8a8c9e1885b4a560b10d39d","tid":550033,"uid":132038,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-04T11:13:25.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-04T11:21:18.000Z","msg":"其實就咁用肉眼睇  好難分    除左仔細去睇下有無花紋太陽紋<br />\n<br />\n你只係會睇到立立靚<br />\n<br />\n某D顏色就會睇到好似有一層玻璃包住咁<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n鍍膜同打臘個分別   <br />\n<br />\n就係打臘唔會幫你去紋去漬  只會幫你車一層臘上架車到  令到架車立立靚<br />\n維持得幾個月<br />\n<br />\n而鍍膜<br />\n就會幫你執到架車靚一靚去晒紋   再幫你上一層鍍膜<br />\n果層鍍膜會凝結成一層保護層去抗UV 防塵等等   令你架車既車漆得到保護<br />\n而比較持久  通常半衰期有1年到2年  視乎你平時點打理架車"},{"pid":"dd0dfc873afb903ffedd5fd6f75c0c0687ad38b0","tid":550033,"uid":63075,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"b87c1a62ae0ec6edb7d036d816c7fff31cb28120","tid":550033,"uid":16058,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-04T11:17:12.000Z","msg":"巴打點睇鍍晶XX<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ?搵火堅唔堅其實 好驚只係GIMMIK野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-04T11:31:11.000Z","msg":"鍍膜通常做晒事前功夫再用人手上一PART一PART咁上<br />\n一定會有不均勻<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/02/04/192557_f753c3a75140ef4445b7e6826161c842.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F02%2F04%2F192557_f753c3a75140ef4445b7e6826161c842.png&h=dd3e14e9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n我求其畫的<br />\n紅色係鍍膜  黑係車漆<br />\n<br />\n用火/用紅外線  去照佢 用外在因素去加快佢乾/凝結<br />\n一定會比普通自然風乾既鍍膜靚<br />\n<br />\n原理就同你去噴油  /焗油  差唔多   焗油一定貴D靚D<br />\n<br />\n因為外在熱力令佢表面自然熔化,凝結<br />\n<br />\n佢就會自然咁去填補凹凸不平既地方   令表面更平均<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n但我會話你知   直接用燈照好撚過啦<br />\n<br />\n用把咁柒細既火槍 係度掃下掃下      一定無照燈咁好<br />\n<br />\n根本只係GIMMIK野    用黎吸引你地"},{"pid":"95bbe9b15f654a691ae92b62ae9ae3dfa3721604","tid":550033,"uid":16058,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"dd0dfc873afb903ffedd5fd6f75c0c0687ad38b0","tid":550033,"uid":63075,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"b87c1a62ae0ec6edb7d036d816c7fff31cb28120","tid":550033,"uid":16058,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-04T11:17:12.000Z","msg":"巴打點睇鍍晶XX<img src=\"/assets/faces/n