sg":"唉.我都比人呃過<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4e5c4d050aaf00e12c45666c54525c1f61f48c96","tid":550033,"uid":16058,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e9fbe6a9cdc487ed401fdbfb343df44be9d3cae9","tid":550033,"uid":11591,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2018-02-05T04:21:25.000Z","msg":"巴打, 想問下依間睇落掂唔掂? <br />\n我見佢基本做齊巴打你講既流程, 係搵唔到佢係用咩牌子鍍膜姐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n因為我住附近, 成日行過見到佢地好多車做, <br />\n做完出黎有燈射住真係好靚, 係唔知可以keep幾耐<br />\nbtw 有無巴打係依間做過<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.bullscoating.com/coating%EF%BC%8Fprocess/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.bullscoating.com%2Fcoating%25EF%25BC%258Fprocess%2F&d=alaECXlSwFpfQY0npZXDsgdLCpCjoNGxXEizPMjNmRM%3D&h=2613f5cd\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.bullscoating.com/coating%EF%BC%8Fprocess/</a>"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-05T04:54:16.000Z","msg":"佢POST出黎D步驟同樓主講要做既野都差不多 留名學野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"85f3494af9352b57c26f1f918792305f1f0f484a","tid":550033,"uid":6875,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-05T07:28:46.000Z","msg":"做完鍍膜<br />\n入停車場泵把簽左個名<br />\n應該噴油後再全車做一次鍍膜？<br />\n本身幫襯開間嘢話一年返去執一次"},{"pid":"776b4ab84d87d91a726a6b3feb01e5cf5542fcbb","tid":550033,"uid":63075,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"ff5580a863b67ee422d65adc31db35dbb359189b","tid":550033,"uid":141205,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-02-04T18:20:00.000Z","msg":"想問下有無辦法check到層鍍膜無哂未？我半年前左右做佢話keep到一年，但而家睇落好似已經無咁有光澤"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-05T08:44:08.000Z","msg":"如果熟悉鍍膜<br />\n有鍍膜定 無左 ,摸落去質感係唔同   會比較滑<br />\n<br />\n維持光澤方面每隻鍍膜會有差,但其實所有鍍膜剛剛做完出黎<br />\n都唔會話維持到成年都咁有光澤<br />\n通常都係得頭幾個月(仲要睇你點保養架車,泊室內外各因素)<br />\n<br />\n但要記住<br />\n就算 無以前咁有光澤,都唔代表層鍍膜無哂<br />\n最簡單既方法就係 有塵,有污垢既情況下   用水射下佢<br />\n如果唔洗你抹   就咁用水就射得甩D塵,污垢<br />\n<br />\n所以點解坊間就算幾貴既鍍膜都好   咩5年期,3年期<br />\n其實都係要每9個月/1年  返去比錢等人幫你上返D鍍腋保養劑,執執佢<br />\n<br />\n如果唔係邊有可能咩5年期呀....屌你老母   香港鍍膜都唔知流行左有無5年"},{"pid":"b116e7eb3447e4af6fb08acada0ce65163d8e200","tid":550033,"uid":63075,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"85f3494af9352b57c26f1f918792305f1f0f484a","tid":550033,"uid":6875,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-05T07:28:46.000Z","msg":"做完鍍膜<br />\n入停車場泵把簽左個名<br />\n應該噴油後再全車做一次鍍膜？<br />\n本身幫襯開間嘢話一年返去執一次"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-05T08:48:31.000Z","msg":"如果係泵把   我會建議你唔好晒錢做多次鍍膜<br />\n噴油果度會幫你用砂紙執完先噴<br />\n<br />\n等下一次返去做保養就得<br />\n<br />\n因為其實平時你做鍍膜     <br />\n泵把位,裙邊人地都係唔會好用心咁去做(特別係你先比得幾千蚊!)"},{"pid":"56fae4d01d6aa54a99bcd6ea5aeba4e1bbee177f","tid":550033,"uid":63075,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f5b87c0902227abaefc8fd77918bb6f06b23c19e","tid":550033,"uid":8100,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-04T19:09:41.000Z","msg":"點解無用日本野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n真心<br />\n用過好多隻，日本野最堅"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-05T08:54:24.000Z","msg":"我打工話唔到事<br />\n用邊隻係上面決定<br />\n可能係成本問題?總之老闆實有佢考量<br />\n<br />\n我老闆9UP 就話日本野剛剛做出黎<br />\n效果係誇啦啦   好靚<br />\n但長遠睇   其實同台灣出品差唔多<br />\n反而你一開始太靚   但唔夠半年就睇唔到   個差落更大   <br />\n而且聽聞出過事 <br />\n<br />\n最最最重要      係我認為<br />\n北美地區   無大中華地區咁祟日   <br />\n出得起錢價 寧願簡英德美產品<br />\n平民就用返台灣韓國"},{"pid":"0d377322539dc7556fbbf4bdbe133c61e6f8e46c","tid":550033,"uid":63075,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"103996dbf0db41b7d9136d481a1259381476c3ea","tid":550033,"uid":2346,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-05T01:49:13.000Z","msg":"點睇autoglym呢個牌子<br />\n樓主可唔可以講下點睇d人打蠟研磨技術好唔好"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-05T09:06:03.000Z","msg":"autoglym呢個牌子<br />\n無用過  答你唔到<br />\n<br />\n點睇d人打蠟研磨技術好唔好<br />\n外行人其實好難睇<br />\n只可以驗收果時做好D    自備捕紋燈囉<br />\n睇下佢有無執漏<br />\n最唔係提早去現場    <br />\n趕係佢地上鍍膜之前<br />\n親眼睇住佢地脫脂<br />\n因為脫完脂就容易望清楚個師傅研磨既成果<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n其實車漆好厚    <br />\n要做到剛剛好去紋 而又唔會車到原裝漆過薄  咁先係好技術<br />\n車深D一樣去到紋架~但你架車既車漆就會愈黎愈薄<br />\n你好難睇得出<br />\n<br />\n另外可以留意下個師傅用咩工具  有無針對不同位置 用返相應既&quot;轆&quot;<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n真係咁撚執著   買部哩D囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/02/05/170234_940de3e4ace749b68e843b2f43f4d790.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F02%2F05%2F170234_940de3e4ace749b68e843b2f43f4d790.jpg&h=1ca817a8&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"802a2c5e1eca93f8c1172f6d3a3ef16a993edd0d","tid":550033,"uid":63075,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e9fbe6a9cdc487ed401fdbfb343df44be9d3cae9","tid":550033,"uid":11591,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2018-02-05T04:21:25.000Z","msg":"巴打, 想問下依間睇落掂唔掂? <br />\n我見佢基本做齊巴打你講既流程, 係搵唔到佢係用咩牌子鍍膜姐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n因為我住附近, 成日行過見到佢地好多車做, <br />\n做完出黎有燈射住真係好靚, 係唔知可以keep幾耐<br />\nbtw 有無巴打係依間做過<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.bullscoating.com/coating%EF%BC%8Fprocess/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.bullscoating.com%2Fcoating%25EF%25BC%258Fprocess%2F&d=alaECXlSwFpfQY0npZXDsgdLCpCjoNGxXEizPMjNmRM%3D&h=2613f5cd\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.bullscoating.com/coating%EF%BC%8Fprocess/</a>"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-05T09:13:37.000Z","msg":"唔似呃人<br />\n但有無收貴就唔知啦<br />\n<br />\n做完出黎有燈射住真係好靚&larr;你打撚完光鈉再用咁撚多燈去射住  都一樣好靚架<br />\n<br />\n而且哩D鋪   網上影出黎既相   你係睇唔到好多細節位<br />\n再加上佢地會後期執相   加重味精<br />\n<br />\n你既然住附近   就不防去親身去望下佢地既成品<br />\n ( 你帶埋黃光電筒實比人屌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />    所以簡大晴天  好陽光底下去望下佢地做完出黎既效果)"},{"pid":"cc22aa696375988bbf553afd787212a16cd2cde1","tid":550033,"uid":63075,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b9b68bdd67bed08bc86cde4b264c4b0e7c5875df","tid":550033,"uid":160120,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-05T03:09:03.000Z","msg":"車身如果有碳纖維件 會唔會鍍埋?"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-05T09:15:49.000Z","msg":"鍍就會鍍埋<br />\n因為只係搽上去<br />\n<br />\n但唔會同你拋"},{"pid":"728b7dbd85a464da41a043a827b8c61752545b3c","tid":550033,"uid":11591,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"802a2c5e1eca93f8c1172f6d3a3ef16a993edd0d","tid":550033,"uid":63075,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e9fbe6a9cdc487ed401fdbfb343df44be9d3cae9","tid":550033,"uid":11591,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2018-02-05T04:21:25.000Z","msg":"巴打, 想問下依間睇落掂唔掂? <br />\n我見佢基本做齊巴打你講既流程, 係搵唔到佢係用咩牌子鍍膜姐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n因為我住附近, 成日行過見到佢地好多車做, <br />\n做完出黎有燈射住真係好靚, 係唔知可以keep幾耐<br />\nbtw 有無巴打係依間做過<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.bullscoating.com/coating%EF%BC%8Fprocess/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.bullscoating.com%2Fcoating%25EF%25BC%258Fprocess%2F&d=alaECXlSwFpfQY0npZXDsgdLCpCjoNGxXEizPMjNmRM%3D&h=2613f5cd\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.bullscoating.com/coating%EF%BC%8Fprocess/</a>"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-05T09:13:37.000Z","msg":"唔似呃人<br />\n但有無收貴就唔知啦<br />\n<br />\n做完出黎有燈射住真係好靚&larr;你打撚完光鈉再用咁撚多燈去射住  都一樣好靚架<br />\n<br />\n而且哩D鋪   網上影出黎既相   你係睇唔到好多細節位<br />\n再加上佢地會後期執相   加重味精<br />\n<br />\n你既然住附近   就不防去親身去望下佢地既成品<br />\n ( 你帶埋黃光電筒實比人屌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />    所以簡大晴天  好陽光底下去望下佢地做完出黎既效果)"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-05T10:17:57.000Z","msg":"好 thanks 巴打 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b7347b9b8b343d5a563616623bb92e4bc0c91536","tid":550033,"uid":3966,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-05T11:51:04.000Z","msg":"巴打咩city做?"},{"pid":"e1ed82daaf7bb0d3ed3eaf604bf372bcf4b79bec","tid":550033,"uid":6875,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b116e7eb3447e4af6fb08acada0ce65163d8e200","tid":550033,"uid":63075,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"85f3494af9352b57c26f1f918792305f1f0f484a","tid":550033,"uid":6875,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-05T07:28:46.000Z","msg":"做完鍍膜<br />\n入停車場泵把簽左個名<br />\n應該噴油後再全車做一次鍍膜？<br />\n本身幫襯開間嘢話一年返去執一次"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-05T08:48:31.000Z","msg":"如果係泵把   我會建議你唔好晒錢做多次鍍膜<br />\n噴油果度會幫你用砂紙執完先噴<br />\n<br />\n等下一次返去做保養就得<br />\n<br />\n因為其實平時你做鍍膜     <br />\n泵把位,裙邊人地都係唔會好用心咁去做(特別係你先比得幾千蚊!)"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-05T13:27:29.000Z","msg":"Thanks 巴打<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"205a01565aa19f7ff1efabb0185ad618a65fe797","tid":550033,"uid":55299,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-05T16:20:53.000Z","msg":"金x時 泡菜野 巴打點睇 早兩三年做過<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3e3bea9e98b6a721bfd66f4ab75f779435906440","tid":550033,"uid":1863,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-05T18:25:01.000Z","msg":"靠汽車工程類嘅嘢移民過黎會否好難？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f19c21381b083f5234e87046b0fa84f22d355c10","tid":550033,"uid":16291,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-05T21:33:17.000Z","msg":"新界區有冇介紹"},{"pid":"28cd534c25a3ef81714f769db3a4ee75d7d84b25","tid":550033,"uid":63075,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"3e3bea9e98b6a721bfd66f4ab75f779435906440","tid":550033,"uid":1863,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-05T18:25:01.000Z","msg":"靠汽車工程類嘅嘢移民過黎會否好難？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-06T01:50:18.000Z","msg":"首先你要係加拿大讀1、2年相關英文証書<br />\n因為唔承認歐美以外地區<br />\n<br />\n再有當地相關工作經驗1年（用工簽）<br />\n<br />\n再搵到顧主幫你擔保<br />\n<br />\n同ielts 符合最值要求<br />\n<br />\n最後移民分數總共超過400分就有機會<br />\n<br />\n視乎學歷、工作經驗、語文能力、年齡多項因素"},{"pid":"1d3b653cca656be8d2b3c15f4cdf171d323c79db","tid":550033,"uid":62297,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"28cd534c25a3ef81714f769db3a4ee75d7d84b25","tid":550033,"uid":63075,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"3e3bea9e98b6a721bfd66f4ab75f779435906440","tid":550033,"uid":1863,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-05T18:25:01.000Z","msg":"靠汽車工程類嘅嘢移民過黎會否好難？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-06T01:50:18.000Z","msg":"首先你要係加拿大讀1、2年相關英文証書<br />\n因為唔承認歐美以外地區<br />\n<br />\n再有當地相關工作經驗1年（用工簽）<br />\n<br />\n再搵到顧主幫你擔保<br />\n<br />\n同ielts 符合最值要求<br />\n<br />\n最後移民分數總共超過400分就有機會<br />\n<br />\n視乎學歷、工作經驗、語文能力、年齡多項因素"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-06T05:44:26.000Z","msg":"樓主係咩city做, 有興趣幫親<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c8f2361177adfcb465d2112d4463622f6cf811c2","tid":550033,"uid":8100,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"56fae4d01d6aa54a99bcd6ea5aeba4e1bbee177f","tid":550033,"uid":63075,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f5b87c0902227abaefc8fd77918bb6f06b23c19e","tid":550033,"uid":8100,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-04T19:09:41.000Z","msg":"點解無用日本野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n真心<br />\n用過好多隻，日本野最堅"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-05T08:54:24.000Z","msg":"我打工話唔到事<br />\n用邊隻係上面決定<br />\n可能係成本問題?總之老闆實有佢考量<br />\n<br />\n我老闆9UP 就話日本野剛剛做出黎<br />\n效果係誇啦啦   好靚<br />\n但長遠睇   其實同台灣出品差唔多<br />\n反而你一開始太靚   但唔夠半年就睇唔到   個差落更大   <br />\n而且聽聞出過事 <br />\n<br />\n最最最重要      係我認為<br />\n北美地區   無大中華地區咁祟日   <br />\n出得起錢價 寧願簡英德美產品<br />\n平民就用返台灣韓國"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-06T08:26:44.000Z","msg":"您老闆係台灣人？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n唔係崇日，事實真係日本野好<br />\n有無用過pika rain?<br />\n呢隻都屌打哂好多出面幫人做coating d鋪<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"376cb9e0062804ea569089db40e4163f0311b2c6","tid":550033,"uid":8100,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e9fbe6a9cdc487ed401fdbfb343df44be9d3cae9","tid":550033,"uid":11591,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2018-02-05T04:21:25.000Z","msg":"巴打, 想問下依間睇落掂唔掂? <br />\n我見佢基本做齊巴打你講既流程, 係搵唔到佢係用咩牌子鍍膜姐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n因為我住附近, 成日行過見到佢地好多車做, <br />\n做完出黎有燈射住真係好靚, 係唔知可以keep幾耐<br />\nbtw 有無巴打係依間做過<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.bullscoating.com/coating%EF%BC%8Fprocess/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.bullscoating.com%2Fcoating%25EF%25BC%258Fprocess%2F&d=alaECXlSwFpfQY0npZXDsgdLCpCjoNGxXEizPMjNmRM%3D&h=2613f5cd\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.bullscoating.com/coating%EF%BC%8Fprocess/</a>"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-06T08:31:54.000Z","msg":"有朋友做過，廢事比人話打手<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n個老闆幾好吹<br />\n您入去望下佢d車就知"},{"pid":"6f5c44b79a321edb194da72a2dccfa75e424c35a","tid":550033,"uid":71524,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-02-06T08:41:14.000Z","msg":"如果我架車<br />\n一架就2年冇打蠟，正係平日洗車，又有石仔彈到既花痕<br />\n整個鍍膜係唔係都係冇用？"},{"pid":"2581d9bc32b246e7ea2c55cac4af4617b6dedf47","tid":550033,"uid":8100,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"6f5c44b79a321edb194da72a2dccfa75e424c35a","tid":550033,"uid":71524,"like":0,"di