ime":"2018-02-09T01:34:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ba1474ab16d1c59bc32faf79cef4a847fc5e1b40","tid":550033,"uid":145496,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-09T09:33:04.000Z","msg":"想請教巴打, <br />\n<br />\n做完鍍膜係咪要避免雨水喺車身曬乾, 會起水印?"},{"pid":"ddee5accf30af2662148f10b4257599a806eba18","tid":550033,"uid":103534,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-18T14:45:23.000Z","msg":"首先我覺得價錢反映質素，如果你比2千至3千上門做又唔可以同有門市收成皮幾野嘅比。<br />\n第二學你話齋，底層功夫要做得好起碼要5至6個鍾，上門做，門市做都好，都係好睇睇功夫。<br />\n最後，coating 年期唔好太過樂觀，我個fd晌Gtechniq專門店做左個14k嘅coating，一樣未到半年花晒。<br />\n<br />\n做coating 點解要咁長時間:<br />\n評估架車嘅車漆狀況，大概分為 <br />\n1.差(好撚花，多氧化，但又未入肉)<br />\n2.中(有太陽紋，小花)<br />\n3好(新車漆面)<br />\n<br />\n第一次洗車<br />\n<br />\n之後推泥膠，起晒啲拋光劑拋唔走嘅野(大概1小時，睇架車狀況)<br />\n<br />\n之後再洗車<br />\n<br />\n用膠紙封好車與車漆邊位，避免之後拋到金屬位同膠位<br />\n<br />\n拋光(視乎車漆狀況)<br />\n研磨劑 compound 過程有分<br />\nHeavy cut&gt;medium cut&gt;finishing  <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n洗車，脫脂<br />\n<br />\n再次檢查車漆<br />\n<br />\n上coating <br />\n<br />\n所以，當你比幾多錢人，收到over 價值所在就係驚喜。但如果收千幾就想有成皮野嘅效果就叫貪心。<br />\n冇話咩叫一定好。<br />\n<br />\n伸利:有DIY coating 經驗，閒時幫fd整下<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/02/18/224359_efda7cf32c076e30cc5d35043c7073e9.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F02%2F18%2F224359_efda7cf32c076e30cc5d35043c7073e9.png&h=8edf1b7b&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/02/18/224401_328791776af5a559a5282bf698d1c7b3.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F02%2F18%2F224401_328791776af5a559a5282bf698d1c7b3.png&h=0ccab940&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"a5275fb7718320def54664b1de295db5994ccf7d","tid":550033,"uid":149070,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-18T14:47:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img 